System Maintenance: We will be back online in a few hours

The Aotearoa Genomic Data Repository has been jointly developed by Genomics Aoteoroa and NeSI to provide a secure place for the New Zealand research community to store and share genomic data. Version 1.0 of the repository is up and running, but we are still adding functionality, so you will see ongoing improvements as we implement new features.
